Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 
A Very Merry Mario Maker! ►► http://bit.ly/1OrNajY
Will YOU Press the Button? - I Can't Resist ► http://bit.ly/1k5qRbG

Would you forgo your looks to become super human? Could you sacrifice a few for the good of the many? If all you'd have to do is Press The Button - would you do it?  Steph and I are each taking a stand, trying to convince you to see things our way. Who will you side with? 

Follow all the updates on new episodes of GTLive!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive

Don't have much time but need a quick fix? Check out some of our highlight episodes for hilarious moments from our live streams. Here are a few to get you started.
